vt. will lay special emphasis of \u201cwaste to health\u201d and \u201cwaste to energy\u201d through biogas for villages. This Gobar Dhan Scheme will make villages clean and raise the income of the small and marginal farmers.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}